sequenceDiagram
  participant UART as UART interrupt
  participant Driver as USART driver
  participant Rx as agc_shell_rx_ind
  participant Sem as agc_sem
  participant Shell as agc_shell thread
  participant CLI as agc_cli_cmd
  UART->>Driver: receive char
  Driver->>Rx: dev.rx_indicate
  Rx->>Rx: read device and push ringbuffer
  Rx->>Sem: rt_sem_release
  Shell->>Sem: rt_sem_take wakes
  Shell->>Shell: parse/edit/echo command line
  Shell->>CLI: agc_cli_cmd(argc, argv)
